"title": "1454: theophany",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1454: theophany",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A temporary visible manifestation of the presence and glory of God. This may be in natural phenomena such as cloud or fire, in human form or in prophetic visionary experience.</p>\n<h2>God is manifested in nature</h2>\n<h3>God's presence in storms, thunder and lightning</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:7-Ps18:15\">PSA 18:7–18:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:16\">EXO 19:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:18\">EXO 20:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:5\">JOB 37:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:3-Ps29:9\">PSA 29:3–29:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:18\">PSA 77:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:4\">PSA 97:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:27-Isa30:33\">ISA 30:27–30:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:2\">AMO 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:11\">HAB 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:14\">ZEC 9:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:19\">REV 11:19</a></p>\n<h3>God's presence in volcanic phenomena</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:18\">EXO 19:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:33\">ISA 30:33</a></p>\n<h3>God's presence in earthquakes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:5-Isa29:6\">ISA 29:5–29:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:4-Judg5:5\">JDG 5:4–5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:18\">PSA 77:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:6\">HAB 3:6</a></p>\n<h2>Specific phenomena associated with the presence of God</h2>\n<h3>Fire signifies God's presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:2\">EXO 3:2</a></strong> <em>Fire in particular represents the purity, holiness and unapproachability of God.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:21\">EXO 13:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:18\">EXO 19:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:17\">EXO 24:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev9:24\">LEV 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:14\">NUM 14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:11-Deut4:12\">DEU 4:11–4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:4\">DEU 5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:22-Deut5:26\">DEU 5:22–5:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:20-Judg13:22\">JDG 13:20–13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:3\">PSA 97:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:30\">JOL 2:30</a></p>\n<h3>Smoke signifies God's presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:18\">EXO 19:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:18\">EXO 20:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:5\">PSA 144:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:4\">ISA 6:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:27\">ISA 30:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:30\">JOL 2:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:8\">REV 15:8</a></p>\n<h3>Cloud signifies God's presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:10\">EXO 16:10</a></strong> <em>Cloud and smoke convey the mystery and transcendence of God.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:21\">EXO 13:21</a>EXO <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:9\">19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:15-Exod24:16\">EXO 24:15–24:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:9\">EXO 33:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:5\">EXO 34:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:15\">DEU 31:15</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:2\">LEV 16:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num9:15-Num9:22\">NUM 9:15–9:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:14\">NUM 14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:10-1Kgs8:11\">1KI 8:10–8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:4\">EZK 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:3-Ezek10:4\">EZK 10:3–10:4</a>MAT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:5\">17:5</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:7\">MRK 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:34-Luke9:35\">LUK 9:34–9:35</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:14-Rev14:16\">REV 14:14–14:16</a></p>\n<h2>God is manifested in human or angelic form</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:7-Gen16:13\">GEN 16:7–16:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:1-Gen18:22\">GEN 18:1–18:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:24-Gen32:30\">GEN 32:24–32:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh5:13-Josh5:15\">JOS 5:13–5:15</a></p>\n<h2>God appears in prophetic visions</h2>\n<h3>God appears on a throne</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:1\">ISA 6:1</a></strong> <em>John interprets this verse to refer to Jesus Christ (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:41\">Jn 12:41</a>).</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:26\">EZK 1:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:1\">EZK 10:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:9\">DAN 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:2\">REV 4:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:11\">REV 20:11</a></p>\n<h3>God appears attended by angels and other heavenly beings</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:2\">ISA 6:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:5-Ezek1:18\">EZK 1:5–1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:9-Ezek10:13\">EZK 10:9–10:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:6-Rev4:11\">REV 4:6–4:11</a></p>\n<h3>God appears like, or with, precious stones</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:10\">EXO 24:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:26\">EZK 1:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:3\">REV 4:3</a></p>\n<h2>Functions and effects of theophanies</h2>\n<h3>Theophanies reveal God's glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:4\">EZK 10:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:10\">EXO 16:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:16\">EXO 24:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:34-Exod40:35\">EXO 40:34–40:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev9:23-Lev9:24\">LEV 9:23–9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:10\">NUM 14:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:11\">1KI 8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:1-2Chr7:3\">2CH 7:1–7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:3\">PSA 29:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:9\">PSA 29:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:2-Ps97:6\">PSA 97:2–97:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:22-Ezek11:23\">EZK 11:22–11:23</a></p>\n<h3>Theophanies bring judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:27\">ISA 30:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:9-Num12:10\">NUM 12:9–12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:13-Ps18:15\">PSA 18:13–18:15</a></p>\n<h3>Theophanies arouse the fear of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:16\">EXO 19:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:18-Exod20:20\">EXO 20:18–20:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:5\">ISA 6:5</a></p>\n<h3>Theophanies commission God's servants</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:8\">ISA 6:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:28-Ezek2:1\">EZK 1:28–2:1</a></p>\n<h3>Theophanies authenticate God's servants</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:5-Num12:8\">NUM 12:5–12:8</a></p>",
